<s> i am not going to object to that , but i would note the anomaly in parliament being able to devote half an hour 's discussion to football hooliganism - and i am nonetheless a great football enthusiast - but not having a spare minute to discuss the biggest form of hooliganism we have , namely the presence of nuclear weapons in the world . </s>
