<s> mr president , i quite understand that you want to avoid a long debate now , but i do not think it was clear when we decided on this this morning that the urgencieswould simply go by the board . </s>
<s> if that had been the case , some members might have voted differently . </s>
<s> this house should certainly not get into the habit of letting subjects which have been on the agenda since the beginning of the week go by the board . </s>
