<s> madam president , as you may well expect , we will not enter into a debate between french and british beef producers now . however , i have two questions to ask . </s>
<s> firstly , could the same checks be carried out for parliament in brussels ? </s>
<s> secondly , in accordance with the precautionary principle , can brussels continue to be a place of work for parliament since it is not equipped with air purifiers ? </s>
