<s> i have two criticisms of the framework agreement . it does not solve those problems typically faced by meps . </s>
<s> one of the problems is that , when we sit in a committee and discuss a bill , the representatives from the different member states , including trainees from the permanent representations who sit behind us , have the ' restrained ' editions of the documents which we are debating but which , as meps , we ourselves are not entitled to receive . </s>
<s> it is a humiliating situation when students are sent documents to which we ourselves do not have access . </s>
<s> another typical problem , which the framework agreement does not solve either , is that we often find ourselves in a situation in which we are able to read in the daily newspaper about a document which has been leaked from the commission . </s>
